Bandits have again launched an attack on the Kaduna-Abuja road restricting movement in the axis.This was made known by former Kaduna State Senator, Shehu Sani, who stated this in a post on his Twitter handle. 

File photo used to illustrate story.



According to Sani, the bandits have caused a road blockage causing travellers to turn back. He tweeted, “Just got a distress call that Bandits in large numbers have again blocked the Kaduna-Abuja road this afternoon. Travellers are speedily turning backwards.” Just got a distress call that Bandits in large numbers have again blocked the Kaduna-Abuja road this afternoon.Travellers are speedily turning backwards. 